title: Phishing Attack Impersonates Travel Brands Using 4,300 Malicious Domains

content.raw: A Russian-speaking threat actor has orchestrated an extensive phishing campaign that has registered over 4,300 malicious domains targeting travelers since the beginning of 2025.
